WHEREAS the Chemical Engineering Students’ Society (ChESS) has submitted a written request for an advance to support participation in the 2025 Canadian Chemical Engineering Conference, as outlined in the attached letter;
WHEREAS Section 6.5.3 of the Sub-Association Policy permits Sub-Associations to request advances of up to two semesters’ expected disbursements, provided sufficient funds are available and a written justification is given;
WHEREAS based on current 2024-2025 enrolment figures, ChESS is projected to receive approximately $2,378.87 in fall and winter levy disbursements this year;
BE IT RESOLVED THAT the Officers approve an advance of $2,300 to ChESS, pursuant to the Sub-Association Policy, to be deducted from future levy disbursements.
